{"idRevelationType":"Mekah","idNameTranslation":"Negeri","number":90,"name":"سورة البلد","englishName":"Al-Balad","englishNameTranslation":"The City","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":20,"ayahs":[{"number":6024,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6024","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6024.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6024.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ لَآ أُقْسِمُ بِهَٰذَا ٱلْبَلَدِ","latin":"Laaa uqsimu bihaazal balad","en":"I swear by this city, Makkah -","id":"Aku benar-benar bersumpah dengan kota ini (Mekah),"},"numberInSurah":1,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6025,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6025","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6025.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6025.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَأَنتَ حِلٌّۢ بِهَٰذَا ٱلْبَلَدِ","latin":"Wa anta hillum bihaazal balad","en":"And you, [O Muhammad], are free of restriction in this city -","id":"dan kamu (Muhammad) bertempat di kota Mekah ini,"},"numberInSurah":2,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6026,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6026","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6026.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6026.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَوَالِدٍۢ وَمَا وَلَدَ","latin":"Wa waalidinw wa maa walad","en":"And [by] the father and that which was born [of him],","id":"dan demi bapak dan anaknya."},"numberInSurah":3,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6027,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6027","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6027.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6027.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"لَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا ٱلْإِنسَٰنَ فِى كَبَدٍ","latin":"Laqad khalaqnal insaana fee kabad","en":"We have certainly created man into hardship.","id":"Sesungguhnya Kami telah menciptakan manusia berada dalam susah payah."},"numberInSurah":4,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6028,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6028","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6028.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6028.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَيَحْسَبُ أَن لَّن يَقْدِرَ عَلَيْهِ أَحَدٌۭ","latin":"Ayahsabu al-lai yaqdira 'alaihi ahad","en":"Does he think that never will anyone overcome him?","id":"Apakah manusia itu menyangka bahwa sekali-kali tiada seorangpun yang berkuasa atasnya?"},"numberInSurah":5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6029,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6029","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6029.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6029.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"يَقُولُ أَهْلَكْتُ مَالًۭا لُّبَدًا","latin":"Yaqoolu ahlaktu maalal lubadaa","en":"He says, \"I have spent wealth in abundance.\"","id":"Dan mengatakan: \"Aku telah menghabiskan harta yang banyak\"."},"numberInSurah":6,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6030,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6030","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6030.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6030.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَيَحْسَبُ أَن لَّمْ يَرَهُۥٓ أَحَدٌ","latin":"Ayahsabu al lam yarahooo ahad","en":"Does he think that no one has seen him?","id":"Apakah dia menyangka bahwa tiada seorangpun yang melihatnya?"},"numberInSurah":7,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6031,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6031","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6031.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6031.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَلَمْ نَجْعَل لَّهُۥ عَيْنَيْنِ","latin":"Alam naj'al lahoo 'aynayn","en":"Have We not made for him two eyes?","id":"Bukankah Kami telah memberikan kepadanya dua buah mata,"},"numberInSurah":8,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6032,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6032","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6032.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6032.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَلِسَانًۭا وَشَفَتَيْنِ","latin":"Wa lisaananw wa shafatayn","en":"And a tongue and two lips?","id":"lidah dan dua buah bibir."},"numberInSurah":9,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6033,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6033","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6033.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6033.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَهَدَيْنَٰهُ ٱلنَّجْدَيْنِ","latin":"Wa hadaynaahun najdayn","en":"And have shown him the two ways?","id":"Dan Kami telah menunjukkan kepadanya dua jalan,"},"numberInSurah":10,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6034,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6034","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6034.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6034.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"فَلَا ٱقْتَحَمَ ٱلْعَقَبَةَ","latin":"Falaq tahamal-'aqabah","en":"But he has not broken through the difficult pass.","id":"Tetapi dia tiada menempuh jalan yang mendaki lagi sukar."},"numberInSurah":11,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6035,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6035","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6035.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6035.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْعَقَبَةُ","latin":"Wa maaa adraaka mal'aqabah","en":"And what can make you know what is [breaking through] the difficult pass?","id":"Tahukah kamu apakah jalan yang mendaki lagi sukar itu?"},"numberInSurah":12,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6036,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6036","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6036.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6036.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"فَكُّ رَقَبَةٍ","latin":"Fakku raqabah","en":"It is the freeing of a slave","id":"(yaitu) melepaskan budak dari perbudakan,"},"numberInSurah":13,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6037,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6037","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6037.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6037.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَوْ إِطْعَٰمٌۭ فِى يَوْمٍۢ ذِى مَسْغَبَةٍۢ","latin":"Aw it'aamun fee yawmin zee masghabah","en":"Or feeding on a day of severe hunger","id":"atau memberi makan pada hari kelaparan,"},"numberInSurah":14,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6038,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6038","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6038.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6038.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"يَتِيمًۭا ذَا مَقْرَبَةٍ","latin":"Yateeman zaa maqrabah","en":"An orphan of near relationship","id":"(kepada) anak yatim yang ada hubungan kerabat,"},"numberInSurah":15,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6039,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6039","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6039.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6039.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَوْ مِسْكِينًۭا ذَا مَتْرَبَةٍۢ","latin":"Aw miskeenan zaa matrabah","en":"Or a needy person in misery","id":"atau kepada orang miskin yang sangat fakir."},"numberInSurah":16,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6040,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6040","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6040.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6040.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"ثُمَّ كَانَ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَتَوَاصَوْا۟ بِٱلصَّبْرِ وَتَوَاصَوْا۟ بِٱلْمَرْحَمَةِ","latin":"Summa kaana minal lazeena aamanoo wa tawaasaw bissabri wa tawaasaw bilmarhamah","en":"And then being among those who believed and advised one another to patience and advised one another to compassion.","id":"Dan dia (tidak pula) termasuk orang-orang yang beriman dan saling berpesan untuk bersabar dan saling berpesan untuk berkasih sayang."},"numberInSurah":17,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6041,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6041","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6041.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6041.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ أَصْحَٰبُ ٱلْمَيْمَنَةِ","latin":"Ulaaa'ika As-haabul maimanah","en":"Those are the companions of the right.","id":"Mereka (orang-orang yang beriman dan saling berpesan itu) adalah golongan kanan."},"numberInSurah":18,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6042,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6042","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6042.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6042.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا هُمْ أَصْحَٰبُ ٱلْمَشْـَٔمَةِ","latin":"Wallazeena kafaroo bi aayaatinaa hum as-haabul Mash'amah","en":"But they who disbelieved in Our signs - those are the companions of the left.","id":"Dan orang-orang yang kafir kepada ayat-ayat Kami, mereka itu adalah golongan kiri."},"numberInSurah":19,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false},{"number":6043,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6043","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6043.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6043.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"عَلَيْهِمْ نَارٌۭ مُّؤْصَدَةٌۢ","latin":"Alaihim naarum mu'sadah","en":"Over them will be fire closed in.","id":"Mereka berada dalam neraka yang ditutup rapat."},"numberInSurah":20,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":594,"ruku":532,"hizbQuarter":238,"sajda":false}]}